443
00:20:40,699 --> 00:20:42,492
Cuci piringnya
selagi kau di sana, Dasar Jalang.

444
00:20:43,202 --> 00:20:47,538
Cuci piringnya
selagi kau di sana, Dasar Jalang.

445
00:20:47,539 --> 00:20:48,748
Cuci piringnya selagi kau di sana,

446
