625
00:28:30,544 --> 00:28:33,129
Dusty. Dusty Boyd. Hammer.

626
00:28:33,130 --> 00:28:35,464
- Ya, Sob. Putra Chuck. Ya.
- Ya, putra Chuck.

627
00:28:35,465 --> 00:28:38,176
